  Script: Fisher_Exact.rexx

  Test: @{B}Friedman analysis of variance by rank test@{UB}.
  Tool: For description and operation select @{"here" LINK FRIEDMAN}.
  Script: Friedman_Rank.rexx

  Test: @{B}Spearman's rank correlation between two variables@{UB}.
  Tool: For description and operation select @{"here" LINK SPEARMAN}.
  Script: Spearmans_Rho.rexx

  Test: @{B}Kendall's rank correlation between two variables@{UB}.
