   1     4     3				      4     2     3     1
   2     6     9				      1     2     3     4
   5     7     9				      1     3     2     4
						      1     2     3     4
						      1     2     3     4

			   Sum of Ranks:	     14    20    26    20
			   Chi-Square:  	    5.4
