@TOC MAIN

@{B}· @{UB}Future versions.
  ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
 This package may still be in development. For those who are aware of
 Microsoft Excel's "Analysis Tools" add-in, this package is intended to be
 a (better) equivalent for TurboCalc.
  
 It is intended that the following additions may be made (if there's a few
 nods of approval!):

 - Probability and critical values for distributions which may still be
   missing. Anyone want to provide the algorithms?!

 - Multiple regression analysis.

 - More non-parametric tests eg. Siegal-Tukey

 - Analysis of circular distributions.

 - Possible specialised test procedures (the Shannon-Wiener biodiversity
   test forms the first of these).

 - Implementation of confidence intervals in tests.
    
 - Possible translation of the documentation into other languages - if
   someone wants to offer! Moi męme, je parle français 'un petit pois'
   (comme on dit en Angleterre..) mais c'est pas bonne... tu vois?ż?

 Suggestions are welcome! For contact details see @{"here" LINK INFO}.

@ENDNODE

